Usage: report_instance_power [-help] [<instance>] [-file <string>]
                             [-inst_file <string>]

-help                   # Prints out the command usage
<instance>              # Specifies the instances to include in the instance
                        # power report (string, optional)
-file <string>          # Writes out the static power analysis report into the
                        # file that you specify (string, optional)
-inst_file <string>     # Specifies multiple instances through a file
                        # (string, optional)